{"tid":1540692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動議撤回就收貨？907 入機場","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:14:57.000Z","uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"581aaa44887595f4e362f11d4d7e2c8ef7721b7c","tid":1540692,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:12:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>動議撤回程序須於10月1日國慶後<br />\n立法會復會<br />\n明顯係想借機過骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以政府之厚顏 <br />\n在美國人權法暫緩和國慶之後再來反口 <br />\n我地一啲都唔意外</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月係機場月，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">九月七再入機場<br />\n一點鐘 機場巴士總站見</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔揸爆春袋，政府都唔會流眼淚</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民旅客look，冇dresscode，拖喼，少量/冇gear，唔嗌口號，搭巴士入機場！<br />\n<br />\n大家見字一人一post幫手傳開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JWvDnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JWvDnu.jpg&h=6ed8b18a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8qsfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8qsfS.jpg&h=4359c0d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbcde550f97739a4cc1482cd6cce76fa6718f5af","tid":1540692,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第六訴求</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Yt9JA.jpg&h=c1d70329&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4okoYBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4okoYBW.jpg&h=be2da638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78ff22bee096739c8bc33a9e739fa9eacd5ea7cd","tid":1540692,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n但我唔想每一次都要抗爭政府先會聽我講野<br />\n所以寫左係基本法既雙普選係一定要有！<br />\n若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變做到!<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"}]}